LogicalTableSource.name: Fact_W_CAMP_HIST_F
LogicalTableSource.Description:
W_CAMP_HIST_F is at the grain of Campain Load Wave-Contact Works with the following Dimensions: Account, Contact, Marketing Source, Campaign Load Wave, Campaign Start date, Campaign Launch Date, Campaign End Date, Campaign Wave Loaunch Date, Marketing Region, Segment, Call Status, E-Mail Bounce Reason, E-Mail Bounce Type
It cannot be used with Offer.
